README for quagga

REQUIREMENTS
http://www.ru.quagga.net/docs/quagga.html#SEC13

This port contains zebra and bgpd rc-scripts only. You may need to
create your own for other daemons. You'll also have to edit and rename
provided configuration files.

PRE-INSTALL
To create dedicated user - run pre-install or create one by hand.

POST-INSTALL

RESOURCES
For quagga & SNMP see http://www.quagga.net/docs/docs-info.php#SEC143
